Friendly Reminders:
   -Is your modpack zipped up properly in the root of the zip and in a .zip format (not .rar or .7zip)? [link to sample pack]
   -Is your info.txt properly filled out and all permissions included?
   -Are all extra files not needed for your modpack removed from the .zip?
   -Are both images .png and less than 150KB in size?
   
   
By clicking submit you acknowledge you have full permissions required to distibute your modpack in a public or private manner on the Feed The Beast Launcher.


